<div class="container mt-5">
  <div class="text-center">
      <h1 class="display-4">Create a ChoreChampion Account!</h1>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="text-center">We don't ask for your information.<br/>Here's a random username and password for you, just make sure to save it in your password manager.</div>
