                                  <br/><br/>
                                  <strong>Pack a Punch:</strong> ChoreChampion leverages the power of the knapsack problem, an optimization strategy that selects tasks with the highest value to fit within your available time, ensuring maximum productivity and satisfaction.
                              </div>
                          </div>
                      </div>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
      </div>
